{"tid":1242384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家唔好再質疑掟蛋成效","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:16:14.000Z","uid":263448,"like":53,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"59f55dc6067d49cb61ecc7fb189ff6b0db5b8a81","tid":1242384,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:47:57.000Z","msg":"今次行動成功都係因為612警員太過暴力，先會成功。<br />\r\n621連日字都同612掉翻轉，分分鐘你一暴力，就會成個形勢都掉翻轉！！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n本來雞蛋撞高牆，已經係個好好文宣題材。<br />\r\n而且電視劇，甚至現代，都有唔少掟雞蛋比政權既情節，完全可以提高我地無力者、反對暴政、和平既地位。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n行動升級，不一定要放火掟磗燒車（而且傷唔到警察）。<br />\r\n我地強大武器之一，就係無力，升級無力感，絕對係對政府既致命武器！！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n文宣部成日比人話掟磗好暴力，比次機會比文宣抨擊班弱智仔「嗱！今次無人掟磗啦！之前都係警察兇狠先有人掟咋！」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n621，警方未必會再重演612，你地愈係加強物理攻擊，只會比佢地乘虛而入！！<br />\r\n我地要既係精神攻擊！唔係物理攻擊！"},{"pid":"4917dc32ab19fa15bf25c515b5f346660c8d7fac","tid":1242384,"uid":257422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d06b5bd061252d200d4b7c1207cb332da0c000","tid":1242384,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b268ea7370d61dbe06570dc18d985a15eb9f459d","tid":1242384,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f55f9d19c8160c826474fc991ef2936ec1a8024","tid":1242384,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf2253d1e57522feeaed4f8d6255008f8ff8a61","tid":1242384,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5af724d590ba6ec3a42304fd463276cdccb5185","tid":1242384,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:31:14.000Z","msg":"浪費好多protein"},{"pid":"7b34bfa7ce41b9106297fc77f82247b738f41768","tid":1242384,"uid":80674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:33:46.000Z","msg